sequenceDiagram
    participant Operator as trustyai-service-operator
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Job as lmes-job Pod<br/>(lm-evaluation-harness)
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ModelEP as Model Endpoint<br/>(vLLM/OpenAI/WatsonX)<br/>HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3-compatible Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant PVC as Local Filesystem / PVC
    participant WandB as Weights & Biases<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(220, 240, 255)
        Note over Operator,WandB: Flow 1: Online LM Evaluation Batch Execution
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create LMEval Job<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token<br/>TLS 1.2+
        K8sAPI->>Job: Schedule Pod

        Job->>HFHub: Download models & datasets<br/>GET /api/models, /api/datasets<br/>Auth: HF_TOKEN (Bearer)<br/>TLS 1.2+
        HFHub-->>Job: Model weights + dataset files

        Job->>ModelEP: Send evaluation prompts<br/>POST /v1/completions<br/>Auth: API Key (Bearer)<br/>TLS 1.2+
        ModelEP-->>Job: Completions / loglikelihood

        Note over Job: Compute metrics<br/>(accuracy, BLEU, perplexity, etc.)
        Note over Job: Cache responses in SQLite<br/>(SHA-256 indexed)

        Job->>PVC: Write evaluation results<br/>JSON output files

        opt Experiment Tracking Enabled
            Job->>WandB: Log metrics & results<br/>POST /api/runs<br/>Auth: WANDB_API_KEY<br/>TLS 1.2+
        end

        opt Push Results to Hub
            Job->>HFHub: Push results/samples<br/>PUT /api/repos<br/>Auth: HF_TOKEN (Bearer)<br/>TLS 1.2+
        end
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 220)
        Note over Operator,PVC: Flow 2: Offline Evaluation (Air-Gapped)
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create LMEval Job<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI->>Job: Schedule Pod

        Job->>PVC: Load pre-cached model<br/>from mounted volume
        PVC-->>Job: Model weights (local)

        Note over Job: HF_EVALUATE_OFFLINE=1<br/>Load metrics from local<br/>metrics/ directory

        Job->>PVC: Run evaluation locally<br/>No external network access

        Note over Job: Compute metrics offline<br/>(bundled metric scripts)

        Job->>PVC: Write evaluation results<br/>JSON output files
    end
